title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-4.60 - Transportation
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 14-4.60 - Transportation

State Regulations

During transportation, food utensils, equipment and tableware are to be protected from contamination, including maintenance of hot or cold temperature requirements. Original individual packages do not need to be over-wrapped or covered if the original package has not been torn or broken. Notes
